penginstalan:
sudo apt install nodejs npm default-jdk -y

penginstallan:
sudo npm install -g cordova

pembuatan:
cordova create gps_projek com.ecchan.grabber EcchanSensor

ke lokasi:
cd gps_projek

konfig:
cordova platform add android
cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-geolocation
cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-battery-status

pembuatan file:
nano www/js/index.js



build:
cordova build android


setting path:
export ANDROID_HOME=/usr/lib/android-sdk
export PATH=$PATH:$ANDROID_HOME/tools:$ANDROID_HOME/platform-tools

fix path: entah kenapa eror jir
export PATH=/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin

install android sdk:
sudo apt install android-sdk -y


setting path lagi:
export ANDROID_HOME=/usr/lib/android-sdk
export PATH=$PATH:$ANDROID_HOME/tools:$ANDROID_HOME/platform-tools

download mesin utama:
wget https://dl.google.com/android/repository/commandlinetools-linux-11076708_latest.zip


1. Ekstrak dan Rakit Struktur Folder
# Buat folder pusat SDK
mkdir -p ~/android-sdk/cmdline-tools

# Ekstrak filenya
unzip commandlinetools-linux-11076708_latest.zip

# Tata sesuai kemauan Google (harus masuk folder 'latest')
mv cmdline-tools latest
mv latest ~/android-sdk/cmdline-tools/


2. Setting PATH (Versi Fish Shell):
set -x ANDROID_HOME $HOME/android-sdk
set -Ua fish_user_paths $ANDROID_HOME/cmdline-tools/latest/bin $ANDROID_HOME/platform-tools

terima lisensi:
yes | sdkmanager --licenses

download bahan utama:
sdkmanager "platform-tools" "platforms;android-33" "build-tools;33.0.2"

pergi ke lokasi dan coba lagi:
